    full_error: "error executing cascade step: CORTEX_STEP_TYPE_FILE_CHANGE: Could not successfully apply any edits. Please review the file and try smaller edits that you are more confident about.: chunk 0: target content not found in file\n(1) tags: map[step_type:FILE_CHANGE]\nWraps: (2) attached stack trace\n  -- stack trace:\n  | google3/third_party/gemini_coder/framework/executor/executor.(*Executor).handleStep\n  | \tthird_party/gemini_coder/framework/executor/executor.go:253\n  | google3/devtools/jetski/boq/agent_service/agent.(*SectionBasedMixin).HandlerDecorators.NewStepMetricsDecorator.func1.1\n  | \tdevtools/jetski/boq/agent_service/step_metrics_decorator.go:23\n  | google3/third_party/gemini_coder/framework/executor/executor.(*ExecutionWrapper).asyncHandleStep.func1\n  | \tthird_party/gemini_coder/framework/executor/execution_wrapper.go:317\n  | google3/go/context/detach.Go.func1\n  | \tgo/context/detach.go:250\nWraps: (3) error executing cascade step: CORTEX_STEP_TYPE_FILE_CHANGE\nWraps: (4)\nWraps: (5) attached stack trace\n  -- stack trace:\n  | google3/third_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/applyedit/applyedit.HandleReplaceFileContentWithFallback.func1\n  | \tthird_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/applyedit/apply_edit.go:183\n  | google3/third_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/applyedit/applyedit.HandleReplaceFileContentWithFallback\n  | \tthird_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/applyedit/apply_edit.go:202\n  | google3/third_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/handlers.(*FileChangeHandler).handleEdit\n  | \tthird_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/file_change.go:212\n  | google3/third_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/handlers.(*FileChangeHandler).Handle\n  | \tthird_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/file_change.go:82\n  | google3/third_party/gemini_coder/framework/executor/executor.(*Executor).handleStep\n  | \tthird_party/gemini_coder/framework/executor/executor.go:225\n  | google3/devtools/jetski/boq/agent_service/agent.(*SectionBasedMixin).HandlerDecorators.NewStepMetricsDecorator.func1.1\n  | \tdevtools/jetski/boq/agent_service/step_metrics_decorator.go:23\n  | google3/third_party/gemini_coder/framework/executor/executor.(*ExecutionWrapper).asyncHandleStep.func1\n  | \tthird_party/gemini_coder/framework/executor/execution_wrapper.go:317\n  | google3/go/context/detach.Go.func1\n  | \tgo/context/detach.go:250\nWraps: (6) Could not successfully apply any edits. Please review the file and try smaller edits that you are more confident about.\nWraps: (7) attached stack trace\n  -- stack trace:\n  | google3/third_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/applyedit/applyedit.HandleReplaceFileContentWithFallback.func1\n  | \tthird_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/applyedit/apply_edit.go:184\n  | [...repeated from below...]\nWraps: (8) chunk 0: target content not found in file\n            \342\224\224\342\224\200 Wraps: (9) attached stack trace\n  -- stack trace:\n  | google3/third_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/applyedit/applyedit.applyApplicableChunksToContent\n  | \tthird_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/applyedit/apply_edit.go:351\n  | google3/third_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/applyedit/applyedit.HandleReplaceFileContentWithFallback\n  | \tthird_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/applyedit/apply_edit.go:118\n  | google3/third_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/handlers.(*FileChangeHandler).handleEdit\n  | \tthird_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/file_change.go:212\n  | google3/third_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/handlers.(*FileChangeHandler).Handle\n  | \tthird_party/gemini_coder/framework/handlers/file_change.go:82\n  | google3/third_party/gemini_coder/framework/executor/executor.(*Executor).handleStep\n  | \tthird_party/gemini_coder/framework/executor/executor.go:225\n  | google3/devtools/jetski/boq/agent_service/agent.(*SectionBasedMixin).HandlerDecorators.NewStepMetricsDecorator.func1.1\n  | \tdevtools/jetski/boq/agent_service/step_metrics_decorator.go:23\n  | google3/third_party/gemini_coder/framework/executor/executor.(*ExecutionWrapper).asyncHandleStep.func1\n  | \tthird_party/gemini_coder/framework/executor/execution_wrapper.go:317\n  | google3/go/context/detach.Go.func1\n  | \tgo/context/detach.go:250\n  | runtime.goexit\n  | \tthird_party/go/gc/src/runtime/asm_arm64.s:1424\n              \342\224\224\342\224\200 Wraps: (10) chunk 0\n                \342\224\224\342\224\200 Wraps: (11)\n                  \342\224\224\342\224\200 Wraps: (12) target content not found in file\nError types: (1) *go_utils.withTags (2) *withstack.withStack (3) *errutil.withPrefix (4) *utils.UserFacingHandlerError (5) *withstack.withStack (6) *errutil.withPrefix (7) *withstack.withStack (8) *join.joinError (9) *withstack.withStack (10) *errutil.withPrefix (11) *applyedit.repairFixableError (12) *applyedit.fastApplyFixableError"
